// https://www.namm.org/standards/implementation-guide-/codes-tables/unit-measurement-uom-codes
const UnitsOfMeasure = {
  'BAG': 'Bag',
  'BKT': 'Bucket',
  'BND': 'Bundle',
  'BOWL': 'Bowl',
  'BX': 'Box',
  'CRD': 'Card',
  'CM': 'Centimeters',
  'CS': 'Case',
  'CTN': 'Carton',
  'DZ': 'Dozen',
  'EA': 'Each',
  'FT': 'Foot',
  'GAL': 'Gallon',
  'GROSS': 'Gross',
  'IN': 'Inches',
  'KIT': 'Kit',
  'LOT': 'Lot',
  'M': 'Meter',
  'MM': 'Millimeter',
  'PC': 'Piece',
  'PK': 'Pack',
  'PK100': 'Pack 100',
  'PK50': 'Pack 50',
  'PR': 'Pair',
  'RACK': 'Rack',
  'RL': 'Roll',
  'SET': 'Set',
  'SET3': 'Set of 3',
  'SET4': 'Set of 4',
  'SET5': 'Set of 5',
  'SGL': 'Single',
  'SHT': 'Sheet',
  'SQFT': 'Square ft',
  'TUBE': 'Tube',
  'YD': 'Yard'
}

export const UnitOfMeasureKeys = Object.keys(UnitsOfMeasure);

export default UnitsOfMeasure;
